I plead the blood of Jesus over this nation. The terrorist attacks that I've seen—we say you are brought to justice.

00:46:03.066 --> 00:46:07.439
You are found in the vans, the semi-trucks, and the dump trucks.

00:46:07.440 --> 00:46:43.003
Your plans will fall apart and there will be confusion in the terrorist camp.

00:46:43.004 --> 00:46:57.810
You will not be successful in anything trying to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:46:57.811 --> 00:47:08.261
Father, we pray over President Trump's family and over him as he plays golf—that no drones or secret stealth drones come nigh him.

00:47:08.262 --> 00:47:29.468
We plead the blood over every border. We hold the blood of Jesus over every person trying to cross, and just like Ananias and Sapphira, if it need be, they'll fall over.

00:47:29.469 --> 00:47:50.299
They will not touch our nation. We rise up spiritually like Davids and slay that giant.

00:47:50.300 --> 00:47:55.879
I thank you, Lord, for protection over our land, over football games, national championships, and the Super Bowl.

00:47:55.880 --> 00:47:59.289
Divine protection is over major sporting events, movie theaters, and megachurches.

00:47:59.290 --> 00:48:04.249
We plead the blood over every congregation—Baptists, Methodists, Catholics—every denomination. We cover them in the blood.

00:48:04.250 --> 00:48:04.349
We thank you for divine restoration over America and for the angels pairing away and putting a guard around President Trump.

00:48:04.350 --> 00:48:04.549
Every dark thing will be exposed by the light. The fertilizer will be found; the FBI, CIA, and Homeland Security will find any plot of the wicked.

00:48:04.550 --> 00:48:04.649
You are raising up men and women of God in these agencies who know how to hear your voice.

00:48:04.650 --> 00:48:04.749
Even the ones not born again will hear you and find the plots.

00:48:04.750 --> 00:48:04.949
I thank you for covering this nation. There are still great things to come.

00:48:04.950 --> 00:48:05.049
We thank you that no plague comes nigh us and that we're always in the right place at the right time.

00:48:05.050 --> 00:51:43.003
We plead the blood over the 10th, the 9th, 8th, and all the way to the 20th. Your divine protection is over Inauguration Day.

00:51:43.004 --> 00:51:49.703
Father, we pray over Canada and thank you that Justin Trudeau's days are numbered.

00:51:49.704 --> 00:52:07.807
They will have a godly leader bringing conservative thinking back over Canada, and there will be a major revival there.

00:52:07.808 --> 00:52:40.500
You are no respecter of persons, so bring change to their nation and over Europe for a great move of the spirit.

00:52:40.501 --> 00:52:47.210
We pray for every believer here, that they are healed and whole.

00:52:47.211 --> 00:52:57.396
Their marriages are strong and their wayward children are called in.

00:52:57.398 --> 00:53:02.279
Satan, get your hands off these kids and unsaved loved ones.

00:53:02.280 --> 00:53:19.573
There will be a radical move of salvation where blinded eyes open, deaf ears hear, and the paralyzed get up out of wheelchairs.

00:53:19.574 --> 00:53:42.857
I believe for a divine outflow of the spirit over all of Asia.

00:53:42.858 --> 00:53:52.085
The communistic spirit will be broken and the Iron Curtain will come down in Jesus'name.

00:53:52.086 --> 00:54:14.819
We call forth these governments trying to hold back the move of God; Father, move them out and expose the darkness.

00:54:14.820 --> 00:54:33.286
We receive everything you have for us. Now, I believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit.

00:54:33.287 --> 00:54:42.640
Acts Chapter 2 says he filled them to overflow and they began to speak with other tongues.

00:54:42.641 --> 00:55:21.976
I believe we have that gift today. I'm going to pray in the spirit for a little while and see if the Lord shows me anything.

00:55:21.977 --> 00:58:17.149
Father, we're open vessels. I thank you that you pray through me. That's interesting.

00:58:17.150 --> 00:58:47.607
I just saw someone being tormented in their mind, and the Lord is setting you free from that demonic spirit right now.

00:58:47.608 --> 00:59:49.479
Be free from hearing voices and the things tormenting you. I saw a demonic spirit wrapped around a void.

00:59:49.480 --> 01:03:22.768
Get off of their mind now in Jesus'name. I see Las Vegas again—the pyramid building with the fountains in the front.

01:03:22.769 --> 01:06:14.192
What about that hotel, Lord? Now I see an Eiffel Tower. It's about the people walking on the streets again.

01:06:14.193 --> 01:07:12.385
Now I'm on Rodeo Drive in Beverly Hills. It's the hotel there.

01:07:12.386 --> 01:07:55.480
It's about the spirit of pride and lust—the lust after things.

01:07:55.481 --> 01:08:27.344
This is attacking greed and lust and how they're choosing locations.

01:08:27.345 --> 01:09:20.052
It's about Rodeo Drive where the real wealthy are—a sign of greed and covetousness.

01:09:20.053 --> 01:09:55.999
I was taken across to New York, to a beautiful high-rise on Central Park Avenue.

01:09:56.000 --> 01:11:18.039
These are expensive condos. It looks like a glass building with a view of the park—it's a Trump building.

01:11:18.040 --> 01:12:28.359
It's about a humbling of finances. There's a jealous spirit behind it, trying to take down the American dream.

01:12:28.360 --> 01:13:35.238
And just like that, now I'm in Miami on the beach, and now Orlando and Disney.

01:13:35.239 --> 01:15:35.477
These are major tourist landmarks and big gatherings of people. Jesus, Jesus. We plead the blood.

01:15:35.478 --> 01:17:37.519
We thank you that we see what is to come and that we hear your voice.

01:17:37.520 --> 01:19:34.359
Back to the MGM Grand, the Bellagio, and the fountains. It's about the cars again.

01:19:34.360 --> 01:19:42.973
The thing about Disney is you can't get close with a car; you have to ride that monorail.

01:19:42.974 --> 01:21:19.873
I'm seeing a suicide vest again. So we call these people discovered and uncovered.

01:21:19.874 --> 01:21:32.068
We thank you that people are protected from vests and shooters at the MGM, the Bellagio, and the Delano.

01:21:32.069 --> 01:22:02.807
At the Beverly Wilshire on Rodeo, the hotel at the end, it's a landmark.

01:22:02.808 --> 01:24:54.975
I see the New York building—the Trump building on Central Park. I just saw the Statue of Liberty and what it represents.

01:24:54.976 --> 01:26:17.047
These people's minds are so deceived that they're trying to take down a symbol to make a statement.

01:26:17.048 --> 01:28:03.712
But the glory of the Lord shall rise. We could stay in that vein for a long time, but we'll take a pause.

01:28:03.713 --> 01:28:24.358
The Lord keeps revealing more. This is a period of time to pray over the whole year—it's not all at once.

01:28:24.359 --> 01:28:34.139
They've been planning this for a long time. I said they will strike and strike.

01:28:34.140 --> 01:29:26.698
These are planned events to keep people in a state of fear. What about Europe?

01:29:26.699 --> 01:30:40.234
What about France? I see the Eiffel Tower again. There's more about France and Europe to uncover.

01:30:40.235 --> 01:31:19.017
London Bridge is falling down—we call all hidden things to be revealed in London.

01:31:19.018 --> 01:31:22.737
We pray over Italy. Rome and the Vatican—the landmarks and major churches.

01:31:22.738 --> 01:31:22.937
Father, you cover these nations. Italy—I thank you that all hidden things be revealed.

01:31:22.938 --> 01:34:10.353
I see the Vatican and the massive Notre Dame. They're trying to make a statement.

01:34:10.354 --> 01:36:08.213
I appreciate you all praying with me today. There's more about Europe, but many hands make light work.

01:36:08.214 --> 01:36:30.893
Thousands of us are believing together that we are changing things in the name of Jesus.

01:36:30.894 --> 01:36:47.873
Everyone say, "Amen."We have the ability to call those things that be not as though they were.

01:36:47.874 --> 01:37:04.799
Thank you for joining me. We'll be back tomorrow; I've heard "emergency call"up until the 10th.

01:37:04.800 --> 01:37:41.335
If you're new here, this is my assignment. Like and subscribe to spread this gospel throughout the world.

01:37:41.336 --> 01:41:21.463
Keep a smile on your face and a song in your heart. God bless you all, and we'll see you again soon.

01:41:21.464 --> 01:41:26.393
Glory to God. Thank you, Jesus, for the manifestation of what we're praying for.

01:41:26.394 --> 01:42:14.280
2024 is gone and now we reach for 2025. We thank you, Lord, that we will thrive. Amen, amen, amen. Glory, glory, glory.

